              contactInfo="Includes and runs custom script code. For example, apply a business rule that limits the range of valid values in an &quot;income&quot; column or add values in two columns and calculate the average of the sum.;Microsoft Corporation; Microsoft SQL Server; Microsoft Corporation; All Rights Reserved; http://www.microsoft.com/sql/support;14"
